title: TranslateCAD
description:
Finally you can leverage the power of TranslateCAD and use your favorite CAT-tool to translate drawings in dwg, dxf.

Read the info on the official site on how to use it.

Just unpack the archive to your PC. Any location will do, even a flash chip.

!!!!!!!BTW IT WORKS ON 64-BIT WINDOWS ONLY!!!!!!
IF YOU TRY RUNNING IT ON A 32-BIT WINDOWS PC, IT WILL ASK FOR ACTIVATION CODE,
SO GET THE DAMN 64-BIT VERSION OF WINDOWS (WINDOWS 7 WORKS FINE)

ENJOY! HAPPY TRANSLATING! CHRISTMAS CAME EARLIER THIS YEAR))))
